"41:15:8" : {s: 41, a: 15, w: 8, r: "قول", t: "وَقَالُوا۟", l: "قَالَ", lc: 1618, tl: "waqālū", lb: "কথা বলা",e: "and they said", b: "এবং তারা বলে", f: 60, rm: "to say/speak, to call, to be named, word/speech, utterance, a thing said, greeting, discourse, one who says/speaks. To inspire/transmit/relate/answer/think/profess, emit an opinion on, indicate a state or condition or circumstance. qailun - speaker, indicator."},
